sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant VIEW as Reporting View
    participant SVC as Reporting Service Facade
    participant SEL as Reporting Selectors
    participant DB as Database

    FE->>VIEW: GET /reports/dashboard-summary or /reports/delinquency
    VIEW->>SVC: compute / build
    SVC->>SEL: deterministic report query
    SEL->>DB: org-scoped aggregates
    VIEW-->>FE: stable report contract
